These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | reggae | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, frog
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | cat | frog | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | roller | quad-bike | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | hiking | card-games | fishing |

 #################################

 
