.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, epic, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | epic | disaster |

