.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, video-games, writing
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | writing | dancing |

